Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:13.017 --> 00:00:16.684
Hi! Welcome to Aha Emi Ruchi!

00:00:30.298 --> 00:00:36.312
What are you making next?
Egg Packing Roll

00:00:45.553 --> 00:00:47.926
Ingredients required to make Egg Roll / Egg Wrap

00:00:48.035 --> 00:00:56.867
Eggs, Spring Onions, Chinese Cabbage, Cucumber,
Garlic, Tomato Sauce, Chapati / Roti / Tortilla, Butter

00:01:03.028 --> 00:01:07.040
Heat a pan

00:01:14.959 --> 00:01:24.700
Keep some Chapatis / Rotis / Tortillas ready
(Make without oil)

00:01:28.325 --> 00:01:34.296
Roast the chapatis on the pan

00:01:42.885 --> 00:01:45.594
Turn off the stove

00:01:47.522 --> 00:01:59.814
Make an omelet with no ingredients
and cut it up into pieces

00:02:00.444 --> 00:02:04.293
Add a layer of the omelet pieces on the chapati

00:02:26.239 --> 00:02:34.640
Take a cup of chopped scallions and
a cup of chopped chinese cabbage

00:02:41.591 --> 00:02:44.809
Add a layer of the cabbage
and the scallions

00:02:53.142 --> 00:02:57.243
Add a layer of chopped cucumber

00:03:00.392 --> 00:03:21.035
Get some Hoisin Dip sauce, available in stores

00:03:21.996 --> 00:03:38.796
To make it at home, add some water 
and fried garlic to some tomato ketchup

00:03:42.598 --> 00:03:46.720
Add some of the sauce on the roll

00:03:48.371 --> 00:03:52.969
Fold it like so, evenly

00:03:59.266 --> 00:04:03.488
Repeat the process

00:04:07.755 --> 00:04:13.685
Smear some butter over the folded egg rolls

00:04:23.058 --> 00:04:28.460
Heat the egg rolls in the microwave for 40 seconds

00:04:38.482 --> 00:04:40.918
Take the Egg Rolls into a serving plate

